    "Dock profiles each keep their own pinned apps, trailing items, widgets, and hidden-app list. Switch between them from the small ball at the leading edge of the dock." : {
      "comment" : "A description of how profiles work.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Docky" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Docky"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Docky can periodically check getdocky.com for new signed releases. Sparkle stores these update preferences directly in your user defaults." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Docky puede consultar periódicamente getdocky.com en busca de nuevas versiones firmadas. Sparkle guarda estas preferencias de actualización directamente en tus user defaults."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Docky could not move to Applications" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Docky no pudo moverse a Aplicaciones"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Docky loads action definitions from bundled JSON. Future curated packages can add actions and append menu items at approved insertion points without replacing Docky's core menus." : {
      "comment" : "A description of how the catalog is refreshed.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Docky loads menu definitions from bundled JSON and executes only reviewed action kinds: builtin, applescript, and menuClick. App-targeted AppleScript and menuClick actions may trigger macOS Automation prompts the first time you use them. The catalog format is designed so future curated packages can add actions and append menu items at approved insertion points without replacing Docky’s core menus." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Docky carga definiciones de menú desde JSON empaquetado y solo ejecuta tipos de acción revisados: integradas, applescript y menuClick. Las acciones AppleScript y menuClick dirigidas a apps pueden abrir indicaciones de Automatización de macOS la primera vez que las uses. El formato del catálogo está diseñado para que paquetes futuros curados puedan añadir acciones y elementos de menú en puntos de inserción aprobados sin reemplazar los menús base de Docky."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Docky preferences (every `docky.*` UserDefaults key)" : {
      "comment" : "A description of what data is included in the feedback sent to the maintainer.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Docky Pro" : {
      "comment" : "The title of the product.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "Docky Pro Features" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
